data.description: Check out this charming remodeled one level traditional rambler in Burgunday Village.  Modern upgrades blend seamlessly with cozy features.    One of the bedrooms is converted to the laundry room & would make a great walk in pantry, or office with a bit of creativitiy.  Fenced in, flat, backyard.  Prime location, close to amenities and commuter routes. A perfect blend of comfort and style.   New flooring & carpet with upgraded padding...BRAND NEW ROOF &  BRAND NEW SIDING (both under manufacture warranty).  All of the big ticket items are handled, move right in at settlement!  Schedule your showing now!
